data.description: Picture this: a one-year-old end-unit townhome that's so fresh, it still has that 'new home' smell – welcoming you!  With the nearby rail system, commuting becomes a breeze, and you'll have more time to enjoy your morning coffee in your pajamas. Because who needs rush hour when you have a stylish haven with a side of convenience? So, enjoy this stylish haven as you walk into the beautiful  great room with upgraded stylings of your elegant kitchen, that continue to each level with beautiful bedrooms; modern bathrooms; and finally to your own Primary suite!  We invite you to schedule a showing now because this home will not last long!!!!!! See you soon!  (NOTE: HOA and Condo fees include:  Common Area Maintenance, Exterior Building Maintenance, Lawn Management, Lawn Care Side, Sewer, Trash, Water, Common Grounds)  Seller is offering a home warranty.
